.TH Float.percent 3 2025-12-11 "Tomo man-pages"
.SH NAME
Float.percent \- format as a percentage
.SH LIBRARY
Tomo Standard Library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.BI Float.percent\ :\ func(n:\ Float,\ precision:\ Float\ =\ 0.01\ ->\ Text)
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Convert a number into a percentage text with a percent sign.


.SH ARGUMENTS

.TS
allbox;
lb lb lbx lb
l l l l.
Name	Type	Description	Default
n	Float	The number to be converted to a percent. 	-
precision	Float	Round the percentage to this precision level. 	0.01
.TE
.SH RETURN
A text representation of the number as a percentage with a percent sign.

.SH EXAMPLES
.EX
assert (0.5).percent() == "50%"
assert (1./3.).percent(2) == "33.33%"
assert (1./3.).percent(2, precision=0.0001) == "33.3333%"
assert (1./3.).percent(2, precision=10.) == "30%"
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Tomo-Float (3)
